songs.title: Intro (M.A The Mixtape)
songs.lyrics: MA! This is the fucking mixtape man, prepare your ears for some real shit. Straight outta Brooklyn, you already know what it is. Um, I just wanna thank everybody man. Everybody that supported me through this whole situation, through my music, I appreciate y'all, thank you. I see y'all, trust me. Um I did this for y'all man, I know y'all been waiting- sorry for the wait you feel me, but my mixtape officially drop Halloween 10/31/2014. Shout out to the squad, real life pain gang and we coming baby that's it. Prepare your ears for some good shit. MA haan!
